name: Node "X"
description: Dissrup's first NFT font, Node, designed by Dogukan Karapinar, embraces new forms for type design as it evolves to meet the diverse requirements of the metaverse.  3 editions of 36 characters are available to purchase as 108 individual NFTs. Purchase of each Node NFT includes a perpetual license for the use of the Node font in both personal and commercial projects. Available in OTF, TTF and WOFF formats.  Upon collection of your NFT, please tweet and tag @dissrup1 to receive a download link directly to your Twitter inbox. Alternatively, you can contact clem@dissrup.com with your wallet address to gain access to your Node download link.
